{"tid":1024304,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"想開個免費日文入門班，順便交流下學日文心得","createTime":"2019-02-16T12:38:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-23T17:22:21.000Z","uid":2771,"like":67,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"2ebc523c8853369dd829f74848634b7196c67511","tid":1024304,"uid":2771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T12:38:50.000Z","msg":"如題, 我哋想試下搞興趣班, 比未學過日文/想學初級日文既朋友參加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋兩個都係N1，一個係日本留過學，一個有日文工作經驗<br />\n時間方面應該會喺平日放工後，方便大家<br />\n地點方面，暫定會喺旺角book課室，可能大家要夾返少少租場錢，但求打個和<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為係小組班, 為咗可以令學生進度盡量同步, 每班人數將會係4-6人左右<br />\n\b程度方面，我哋想開入門班先，教五十音, 語彙同基本文法, 之後如果反應好會再考慮開更高程度嘅班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外，如果想搵我哋幫手衝JLPT、或者有其他日文相關嘅問題都可以隨便問，睇吓點幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有興趣可以填 Google form:<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/C5CKBUqmBSCsucav2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2FC5CKBUqmBSCsucav2&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7L5ugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=db525e57\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/C5CKBUqmBSCsucav2</a><br />\n我哋會有專人聯絡你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4dc6e88ab03da38093f30ead04d40e432aee342","tid":1024304,"uid":2771,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T12:39:20.000Z","msg":"有咩問題都可以係度問，答到嘅我哋會儘量答<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68697858e45198d91536d947c44e2579ff8aa8e5","tid":1024304,"uid":2771,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T12:51:48.000Z","msg":"push <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f101596ab5718f9a33be7ffb8e74350e836a5f","tid":1024304,"uid":2771,"like":0,"dis